00:50:14.507 --> 00:50:16.510
Če ni suše,

00:50:19.012 --> 00:50:21.014
je prekleti upor.

00:50:24.434 --> 00:50:26.436
Zatlači mu lijak v usta.

00:50:44.663 --> 00:50:49.041
